OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783952425
OL,3,CPlymouth experts warn of impact of
OL,4,Cmarine heatwave on sea life
OL,6,FThe Met Office says the marine
OL,7,Fheatwave could reach "extreme" levels
OL,8,Faround parts of the UK, which experts
OL,9,Ffrom Plymouth say can impact the
OL,10,Fgrowth and feeding habits of sea
OL,11,Fspecies.
OL,13,FMatt Frost, Head of the International
OL,14,FAffairs Office at Plymouth Marine
OL,15,FLaboratory, describes the sea
OL,16,Ftemperature as "incredibly unusual" at
OL,17,Fthis time of year.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
