OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783952425
OL,3,CPlymouth experts warn of impact of
OL,4,Cmarine heatwave on sea life
OL,6,FMeanwhile, scientists have warned that
OL,7,Fhigher sea temperatures are having an
OL,8,Fimpact on marine life, such as
OL,9,Fplankton and jellyfish.
OL,11,FBryony Squires, Plankton Apprentice
OL,12,Fwith the Western Channel Observatory,
OL,13,Fsays: "Temperatures can accelerate the
OL,14,Fgrowth (of jellyfish) slightly - make
OL,15,Fthem reproduce more quickly, and
OL,16,F(affect) how much food availability is
OL,17,Fthere for them."
OL,19,F"Current, wind, ocean conditions, prey
OL,20,Favailability, temperatures can
OL,21,Finfluence the growth of jellyfish".
OL,26,@vD@HpmvD@UpnxD@ApmxD@Hpn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
