FL,409,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1783952425
OL,3,CPlymouth experts warn of impact of
OL,4,Cmarine heatwave on sea life
OL,6,FExperts say these record temperatures
OL,7,Fare expected to have wide-ranging
OL,8,Fimpacts on weather patterns, the
OL,9,Fglobal climate and ecosystems, driving
OL,10,Fshifts in fish populations and
OL,11,Fdamaging many marine species.
OL,13,FThe hot spell last month saw
OL,14,Ftemperatures break the record for the
OL,15,Fhottest June day ` set 50 years ago
OL,16,Fduring the infamous 1976 summer ` by
OL,17,Fmore than 1C.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
